{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342190/extras/SKY_Launch_Trailer.jpg?t=1667211026\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skyworld</h2><br>Claim command over the VR battlefield! Put the power of a full army \u2013 even dragons \u2013 at your fingertips in Skyworld, the award-winning RTS/TBS wargame for VR from the creators of Arizona Sunshine.<br><br>Imagine a place where worlds dot the sky like stars. Worlds with cores of magic, as old as time though very much alive. Demons, driven by a lust for power, have now spilled into the once prosperous worlds to mine their powerful, magical crystals. Starting out with a small army, you set out on a conquest across the magical Skyworlds to deliver them from darkness.<br><br>Developed from the ground up for VR, Skyworld puts you at the helm of a kingdom at war. Build and command your forces right in the VR world, conquer all Skyworlds in a royal campaign, and wage war against friends in online multiplayer.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Conquer a range of unique Skyworlds in a story-based campaign<br></li><li>Manage your population, buildings &amp; resources right in the VR world<br></li><li>Command your forces in addictive real-time battles<br></li><li>Use your own spells to turn the tide of battle!<br></li><li>Research and upgrade a full roster of army units &amp; legendaries<br></li><li>Select your battle arena of choice and compete in 1v1 online matches</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Your First Skyworld","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/342190/6ed3dbaf769e14c0476a988af83fd93b7bae827c.jpg"},{"name":"Battle for the Crystals","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/342190/6e1ab95adef94cc9f7472bc728acca16b3232157.jpg"},{"name":"Live to Fight Another Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/342190/7adf4ba8530c1101985d5f59